data.title: Happy 45th birthday to Nelly Furtado! A varied artist who embraces many musical genres, she practically owned the 2000s. Her success came...
data.meta_description:
10 likes, 0 comments - insignificantnick on December 2, 2023: "Happy 45th birthday to Nelly Furtado! A varied artist who embraces many musical genres, she practically owned the 2000s. Her success came at a cost, though, as she suffered a nervous breakdown in 2007. As she put it, it was too much too soon. She's kind of stayed out of the spotlight until recently. She looks and sounds as good as ever.
#nellyfurtado #birthday #triphop #dancepop #maneater #canadian #2000s".
